===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# <!--NHalfSphere-->{{geometry}} A half-[[sphere]], formed by a [[plane]] [[intersect]]ing the center of a sphere.
# <!--NHalfPlanet-->{{geography}} Half of the [[Earth]], the [[Northern Hemisphere]], [[Southern Hemisphere]], [[Western Hemisphere]] or [[Eastern Hemisphere]].
# <!--NHalfBrain-->{{anatomy}} Either of the two [[halves]] of the [[cerebrum]].

